  name: "Aura of Truth"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 11th level, the paladin automatically succeeds at saving throws\
    \ to disbelieve illusions of the phantasm) subschool and automatically gains a\
    \ saving throw to disbelieve figment illusions when she observes them. Allies\
    \ within 30 feet gain a +4 bonus on saving throws to disbelieve illusions of the\
    \ phantasm) subschool."
